{"type": "article", "id": 62502, "title": "英国手袋品牌 Anya Hindmarch 易主，以及，上海时装周这些值得一看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2019-03-29T04:26:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3559, "name": "上海时装周"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190329121255FCIo74JlSjTEubem.JPG", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/anya-hindmarch-sold-to-marandi-family?from=2019-03-27&amp;to=2019-03-28\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marandi 家族收购英国手袋设计师品牌 Anya Hindmarch</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Anya Hindmarch 于 1987 年创立，因充满童趣的贴布手袋设计吸引了众多明星和皇室成员的喜爱，2012 年被卡塔尔 Mayhoola 基金收购，后者旗下还拥有 Valentino、Balmain 等品牌。截至去年，Mayhoola 在 Anya Hindmarch 的股权占比已达到 75%，但由于品牌重组困难试图套现。2017 年，该品牌税前净损失达到 3700 万美元。收购者 Marandi 家族此前的投资还包括 Soho Farmhouse 以及 Emilia Wickstead。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Bain-Capital-acquires-majority-stake-in-Maesa,1083758.html#.XJ1xr-szbOQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">贝恩资本收购日化公司 Maesa</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Maesa 为 Becca Cosmetics、Target、H&amp;M 以及 Urban Outfitters 等多个品牌开发、设计、生产和营销美妆、护发以及香水等产品。年销售额达到 2.3 亿美元。贝恩资本未透露此次投资数额。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/411786/dior-fabu-2019-kongshanjizaoqiuxilieguanggaodapian/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dior 发布 2019 早秋系列广告大片。</a></strong></p><p>以日本插画艺术家空山基为灵感。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019032909080874vsfUnAJTtZrl2d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329090807VSRCgEQptyhqzNZP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329090808fQZ2cMwgmuDXLKNJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599700\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>上海时装周于 3 月 27 日至 4 月 6 日举行。</strong></p><p><strong>新天地太平湖主秀场：</strong></p><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.shanghaifashionweek.com/?portfolio_page=xuzhi\" rel=\"nofollow\">XU ZHI 2019 秋冬系列：</a></strong></p><p>XU ZHI 在新天地主秀场发布了首个男女装混合秀。该系列以“消失的缪斯”为主题，空中传来潺潺水声，品牌标志性的提花、编绳和拼接等技法运用在牛仔、羊毛以及针织产品上，也给服装带来了流动的效果。</p><p>配饰来自设计师品牌 Yvmin，部分内衣产品为 XU ZHI 与内衣品牌 NEIWAI 的合作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104437oJNWqdHfRCjLcEuz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.511250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104508y2hQsGn9zXxR8PmB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104440xozvRQ3U7D59rGyc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104444VJTKIg2z6OqxNehy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019032910444483Eqdux5tr60l9g7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104453E5x9FaNAshqQvJX1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903291044540vge4wlSdQ3UW5jH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104456Ix3vQ15WXjHCbZda.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104457XdSEhGy2b7Tsr5k3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104503q4EhmY6AoZ7dKR1z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104504j2CkFAD7bn0zcfxM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903291045051jou3neC4xAJvyaf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104510KT7IV9Ray1Oq6oYg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329104511QdfalJ0FwPszEkCo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.shanghaifashionweek.com/?portfolio_page=8on8-4\" rel=\"nofollow\">8ON8 2019 秋冬系列：</a></strong></p><p>8ON8 本季灵感来自伍迪·艾伦 1973 年执导的科幻喜剧电影《傻瓜大闹科学城》（Sleeper）。伍迪·艾伦在电影中想象了 200 年后人类社会的样子。秀场中央放置着巨大的浅蓝色西瓜、香蕉、橙子和鸡，以还原电影中超生培育农场的情景。</p><p>设计师龚力提取了片中那些既具未来感又带着 70 年代色彩的嬉皮和户外元素，结合电影中出现的超市售货员、警察、工人、居民等角色，塑造多变的男性形象。其中还有一套为与 VISA 的联名款。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113113feyrud9vVg2Fa1mw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113114xsupLXPRtqZ2Wfjm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903291131145zMs6TLGCxj7OtVB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113117N7qMRtYbdjKlPSV9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113120n9rfspVFxIg7KL8U.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113120A4tU2WsQF0ruyHP7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113126VMKsWISQxvjkJzP5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113126jPG9SROn8wbFdZ23.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113127hpAIOcukREUFJds3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113129Qx3BHOFsafJ7YI2L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113130TFyez1AUbcKhpHnj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903291131335DxFG84fvRi97zVS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113136bicErLMKIvSUy3Bw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113136BzmOHqoaeLhWYusx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019032911313986yO4HqBPcpFDE93.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113140Q65d1BVksP9yhM3b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113144uCxHzXwZiqsdycLB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113144Mw8HeFpKkVNRlGfv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113145ZxjEdQgsnLwrNimF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113145moLMbOr0GD8BhwHd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.shanghaifashionweek.com/?portfolio_page=wan-hung-3\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wan Huang 2019 秋冬系列：</a></strong></p><p>设计师把秀场铺满了红棕色树叶，模特们仿佛在秋日的欧洲庄园中散步。反复出现的造型包括夸张的皮质报童帽搭配夸张的皮质西服套装，以及巨大廓形的皮毛一体斗篷和外套。颈部的套索装饰，令人想起不久前因引起争议而下架的 Burberry 创意总监 Riccardo Tisci 的设计。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111127i8XN69jZmHoPnxfp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111128VFLE1NXa2SCHW9j4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111129Ri7v9qBmSYD5Eok0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111130WMabIu7OAEHr4gQC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111135uH8Ri4SQCFx3ckAI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111138ldfbWSwYjBctGvun.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111139WMb5r0VQFnTDKLZv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111144kXIZPhuQHCTMw4zy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111154w40tmu1MjsQlcyYG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111155ehVBNErF2JdHAT1w.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111155XmQdV3xRlaIEt85i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111201fMGiHB1pytsRuIaP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111202aGC9hnrFi0xy4IcE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329111202CzHq1o30mXudwZrD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.shanghaifashionweek.com/?portfolio_page=roderic-wong-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Roderic Wong 2019 秋冬系列：</a></strong></p><p>设计师 Roderic Wong 曾在奢侈品集团F.J.Benjamin 工作，创立同名品牌次年经集团资助在新加坡时装周发布了个人胶囊系列，2016 年在上海创立工作室推出其女装高级成衣线 Roderic Wong。</p><p>不过虽说是设计师品牌，但本季发布的系列却更近似现代商业品牌（contemporary brand）的做法，能找到不少对流行元素的复制，比如长款衬衫侧部收腰的设计、半裙前部通过拉绳制造褶皱效果等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329105957GYe2jCk6IKyco0bz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.573333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329110000SHX8WMZa6I7qcrei.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329110203g0dCX97EMvse14Lt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329105957WUERaAiTDwje0mLQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329105957BjfH1vi3wRDLauTX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903291100035MmEc3lSCrNWxg6F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329110005B8l5WxqRXQ1e6Prm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329110006WFzqPVDXhfvONrke.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329110006RAvH1nK4fUd9soDB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329110009vVjcJ07WqQg5Ni6A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329110225FaA91u02lMeLWrCB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329110230gWdFB7mhq2JXksHZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>独立设计师展区 XCOMMONS：</strong></p><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.shanghaifashionweek.com/?portfolio_page=whm-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">WHM 2019 秋冬系列：</a></strong></p><p>设计师王浩铭希望 WHM 塑造的是将衣服视作一种长久物品的女性，“过多的选择也许并不重要，我们希望用最恰到好处、最简明扼要的设计让女性散发持久魅力”。</p><p>本季可以看到女性衣橱中必备的基本款单品：丝绸衬衫、西服套装、风衣、阔腿裤、V 领针织衫。它们都很日常，但精心选择的配色和材料却又让这些单品呈现出独特质感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113700NkvVOXKHQW4g0cfR.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113701q7y5mn2phcVsOW8P.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113703Df7ZbspiU08d2mBH.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.402597\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113703Htpb2ZaUqMxdE19k.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113704hmKkRAeOI2WTNPM8.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113704RwED3BIJk2UX7AQP.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.402597\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113704ao9kf5CvuRz2hj8p.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113706HaGCieBdS4y6zZEL.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113706Hz8F5svJRmDPpayU.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329113707GD7s8wc1aTrjfVkP.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>HAIZHENWANG 2019 秋冬系列：</strong></p><p>王海震本季主题为“剧院里的现实与梦境综合”，灵感来自皮娜·鲍什的剧场世界。</p><p>上生新所 7 号楼被红色帷幔分隔成两个区域，木质地板和昏暗的黄色灯光共同制造出剧场氛围。</p><p>设计师试图把欧洲剧院建筑的形式与女性气质内核融合，并通过棱角分明的女式西服套装呈现出来。硬朗的肩线和腰线与宽大的水手服领坎肩增添了阳刚气；而白色荷叶边高领衬衫、丝绸格纹长裙以及随处可见的水钻装饰，又增添了带有华贵感的女性特质。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329115308ILGl4SEb6RtmK5FQ.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329115309SzdpTECmYVIu3ZwH.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329115325TwU6iALrBf3gcPuS.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329115326yFiKrLapZQ24S19J.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019032911532849Ip7RFSEmwezT3c.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329115328db3gUxHL084F5uip.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329115329fMCOyPXAL3bdQHlS.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903291153342KL9FUpTgqdrOevo.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329115334bsU1vq4J70APGca5.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>独立设计师展区 Labelhood：</strong></p><p><strong>Susan Fang 2019 秋冬系列：</strong></p><p>设计师本季以“Air·Painting”为主题。灵感来源于她的童年： “我的童年充满了妈妈给我织的毛衣的回忆，小时候穿不下的，毛线会被拆下然后重新组织成新的毛衣。”</p><p>设计师刻意在毛衣上留下破洞，再用手工钩针的绘出花朵和星星的形状。通过“Air-Embroidery”(空气刺绣)技术，不同层次中的刺绣使图案在模糊空间中形成水彩幻影。此外，“Air Weave(空气编织)”手工技术这次尝试以毛线为材料，编织出渐变色和动态格子效果。泡泡配饰系列也与服装融合，透明玻璃珠与纱线交织在了一起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329120111T3XCA8iZE7eMzRh5.JPG\" data-ratio=\"1.501779\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329120112BKX9iRaSEIrg7lqh.JPG\" data-ratio=\"0.667244\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329120111LRgyUeborJ58h6Af.JPG\" data-ratio=\"0.667244\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903291201135igFdSaCIW03KbHE.JPG\" data-ratio=\"0.667244\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329120031rJ1Kt3dSbTwQn0ca.JPG\" data-ratio=\"0.667244\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329120032jqfM21kVFEp9r85X.JPG\" data-ratio=\"0.667244\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329120031i0Tm5nd4KBpC8hXD.JPG\" data-ratio=\"0.667244\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自 XCOMMONS</p>"}